    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Coverings, often textiles, laid on furniture for protection or decoration, used especially to keep heat or scratches from polished surfaces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
